name: Review
query:
SELECT
  `tabQuality Action`.name as "Name:Data:200",
  `tabQuality Action`.action as "Action:Select/[corrective,Preventive]:200",
  `tabQuality Action`.review as "Review:Link/Quality Review:200",
  `tabQuality Action`.date as "Date:Date:120",
  `tabQuality Action`.status as "Status:Select/Planned:150"
FROM
  `tabQuality Action`
WHERE
  `tabQuality Action`.type='Quality Review'
